dct_title_s: Map of the original swamp areas of the lower peninsula of Michigan.: 1907. Compiled from John Farmer's map of 1873 for report
dct_description_sm: By C. A. Davis on peat.
From Geological Survey of Michigan. Annual report for 1906. Plate XVI. Swamp areas shown in brown. 1 map: col.; 64 x 52 cm.
